pullsbody:
Bumps [mysql](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql) from 2.1.1 to 2.17.1.
Changelog *Sourced from [mysql's changelog](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/blob/master/Changes.md).* > ## v2.17.1 (2019-04-18) > > * Update `bignumber.js` to 7.2.1 [#2206](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/2206) > - Fix npm deprecation warning > > ## v2.17.0 (2019-04-17) > > * Add reverse type lookup for small performance gain [#2170](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/2170) > * Fix `connection.threadId` missing on handshake failure > * Fix duplicate packet name in debug output > * Fix no password support for old password protocol > * Remove special case for handshake in determine packet code > * Small performance improvement starting command sequence > * Support auth switch in change user flow [#1776](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1776) > * Support Node.js 11.x > * Update `bignumber.js` to 6.0.0 > > ## v2.16.0 (2018-07-17) > > * Add Amazon RDS GovCloud SSL certificates [#1876](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1876) > * Add new error codes up to MySQL 5.7.21 > * Include connection ID in debug output > * Support Node.js 9.x > * Support Node.js 10.x [#2003](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/2003) [#2024](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/2024) [#2026](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/2026) [#2034](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/2034) > * Update Amazon RDS SSL certificates > * Update `bignumber.js` to 4.1.0 > * Update `readable-stream` to 2.3.6 > * Update `sqlstring` to 2.3.1 > - Fix incorrectly replacing non-placeholders in SQL > > ## v2.15.0 (2017-10-05) > > * Add new Amazon RDS ca-central-1 certificate CA to Amazon RDS SSL profile [#1809](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1809) > * Add new error codes up to MySQL 5.7.19 > * Add `mysql.raw()` to generate pre-escaped values [#877](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/877) [#1821](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1821) > * Fix "changedRows" to work on non-English servers [#1819](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1819) > * Fix error when server sends RST on `QUIT` [#1811](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1811) > * Fix typo in insecure auth error message > * Support `mysql_native_password` auth switch request for Azure [#1396](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1396) [#1729](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1729) [#1730](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1730) > * Update `sqlstring` to 2.3.0 > - Add `.toSqlString()` escape overriding > - Small performance improvement on `escapeId` > * Update `bignumber.js` to 4.0.4 > > ## v2.14.1 (2017-08-01) > > * Fix holding first closure for lifetime of connection [#1785](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mysqljs/mysql/issues/1785) > > ## v2.14.0 (2017-07-25) > > ... (truncated)
Commits - [`33cb884`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/33cb8846d11fd36a267fdb827a42d9ebeaf2f8d6) 2.17.1 - [`f0cb4bb`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/f0cb4bbe7e7fc1adf273567b02779d2c445ffdfa) docs: expand pool acquireTimeout option docs - [`5e96be5`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/5e96be576579ce4b65cf39cccd4e0671d110fdd8) Update bignumber.js to 7.2.1 - [`9f1a655`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/9f1a6553615fb9c9a9957df3a2a027207453fa06) build: Node.js@8.16 - [`946a7a2`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/946a7a2d70881ce8da9918416fb6f5337990d8a7) 2.17.0 - [`5569e02`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/5569e02ad72789f4b396d9a901f0390fe11b5b4e) Add reverse type lookup for small performance gain - [`d916479`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/d9164799f78e17f3700c13e907a66f7510dcbd9d) Support auth switch in change user flow - [`776d843`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/776d8430465865c512fb102a77722477409f894e) build: Node.js@11.14 - [`e5a922b`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/e5a922bb09c4fa4c17997e4195b9f721dbd4ce4d) Update bignumber.js to 6.0.0 - [`5bea43c`](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/commit/5bea43c5336be9b507b64dd8d40232de4b9cd736) build: eslint@5.15.1 - Additional commits viewable in [compare view](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql/compare/v2.1.1...v2.17.1)

pullsbody:
Minimal changes are also necessary on Heroku or wherever it is at the moment.

1) Get the api key from me

2) Add these configs to the Heroku app:
heroku config:set NEW_RELIC_LICENSE_KEY=licensekeyiwillgiveyou
heroku config:set NEW_RELIC_APP_NAME=gitribution-production
heroku config:set NEW_RELIC_APDEX=<0.010>

3) Pull these changes in.

Cheers!
